snippet.title: The cast reveals what they know about Aquaman
snippet.description:
At the Aquaman premiere in Los Angeles, Variety interviewed the Jason, Amber, Patrick, Nicole, Dolph, Yahya and Michael and asked them what they knew about Aquaman before they were cast in the film.
